Eric G. Johnson  President & CEO, Baldwin Richardson Foods Co.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 4 Board Members in 4 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships66--
Background

		Mr. Eric G. Johnson has been the President and Chief Executive Officer of Baldwin Richardson Foods Company since December 1997. Mr. Johnson served as the Chief Executive Officer of Johnson Products Company. A business entrepreneur, in 1992 he went on to purchase Baldwin Ice Cream Co. and expanded the distribution and sales of Baldwin Ice Cream Co., and in 1997. He has been an Independent Director at Lincoln National Corporation since 1998. He serves as Director of Lincoln ... Financial Advisors Corporation. He has been an Independent Director of SUPERVALU Inc. since July 18, 2013. He  serves as a member of the board of directors for the Urban League of Rochester and the board of trustees for Babson College and Rochester Institute of Technology. Mr. Johnson received his bachelor of arts and science degrees in Finance and Management from Babson College. He also holds his master of business administration degree from the University of Chicago, Graduate School of Business.Read Full Background




